OL,3,CHigh Court challenge against Met over
OL,4,CFreemason declaration policy thrown out
OL,6,FA bid by Freemasonry bodies to bring a
OL,7,Flegal challenge against the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police over its decision
OL,9,Fto force officers and staff to declare
OL,10,Fwhether they are or have been
OL,11,FFreemasons has been thrown out by a
OL,12,FHigh Court judge.
OL,14,FMr Justice Chamberlain said on Tuesday
OL,15,Fthat the Met's decision "serves a
OL,16,Flegitimate aim, maintaining and
OL,17,Fenhancing public trust in policing,
OL,18,Fand is proportionate".
