OL,3,CHigh Court challenge against Met over
OL,4,CFreemason declaration policy thrown out
OL,6,FThree bodies representing Freemasons
OL,7,Fin England, Wales, the Isle of Man and
OL,8,Fthe Channel Islands, as well as two
OL,9,Fserving police officers who are
OL,10,FFreemasons, had sought to take legal
OL,11,Faction against the force at the High
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FIt came after the Met announced in
OL,15,FDecember that membership of the
OL,16,FFreemasons or similar organisations
OL,17,Fwould be added to its declarable
OL,18,Fassociations policy.
