OL,3,CHigh Court challenge against Met over
OL,4,CFreemason declaration policy thrown out
OL,6,FThis means officers and staff were
OL,7,Frequired to declare membership "past
OL,8,For present" of any organisation that
OL,9,Fis "hierarchical, has confidential
OL,10,Fmembership and requires members to
OL,11,Fsupport and protect each other".
OL,13,FAround 400 Met officers and staff have
OL,14,Falready made declarations under the
OL,15,Fpolicy.
OL,17,FIn a 17-page ruling on Tuesday, Mr
OL,18,FJustice Chamberlain said the grounds
OL,19,Fof the proposed legal challenge were
OL,20,Fnot "reasonably arguable".
