OL,3,CHigh Court challenge against Met over
OL,4,CFreemason declaration policy thrown out
OL,6,FThe judge continued that the policy
OL,7,Fwas not discriminatory or "unduly
OL,8,Fstigmatising" against Freemasons.
OL,10,FHe added that leaving the decision of
OL,11,Fwhether to declare membership of the
OL,12,FFreemasons to individual officers and
OL,13,Fstaff on an "ad hoc basis" would not
OL,14,F"achieve the object of maintaining or
OL,15,Fenhancing public trust".
OL,17,FFollowing the decision, Commander
OL,18,FSimon Messinger said on behalf of the
OL,19,FMet: "We had been prepared to robustly
OL,20,Fdefend our decision through the
OL,21,Fcourts, so today's judgment is welcome.
