OL,6,F"Our declarable associations policy
OL,7,Fwas changed after feedback highlighted
OL,8,Fconcerns that involvement in these
OL,9,Ftypes of organisations could
OL,10,Fcompromise impartiality or create
OL,11,Fconflicts of loyalty.
OL,13,F"Both victims of crime and those
OL,14,Freporting wrongdoing must have trust
OL,15,Fand confidence there is no risk that
OL,16,Finvestigations are tainted by such
OL,17,Fissues.
OL,19,F"We have prioritised this over any
OL,20,Forganisation's desire to maintain
OL,21,Fsecrecy."
