OL,3,CHigh Court challenge against Met over
OL,4,CFreemason declaration policy thrown out
OL,6,FAt a hearing on February 11, lawyers
OL,7,Ffor the two officers, the United Grand
OL,8,FLodge of England, the Order of Women
OL,9,FFreemasons and the Honourable
OL,10,FFraternity of Ancient Freemasons asked
OL,11,FMr Justice Chamberlain to allow the
OL,12,Fchallenge to proceed.
OL,14,FClaire Darwin KC, for the claimants,
OL,15,Fsaid that the Met's decision allowed
OL,16,Fit to create a "black list".
